T1  - A COMMENT ON “ESTIMATING DYNAMIC DISCRETE CHOICE MODELS WITH HYPERBOLIC DISCOUNTING” BY HANMING FANG AND YANG WANG
AU  - Abbring, Jaap H.
AU  - Daljord, Øystein
Y1  - 2020/05/01
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2020/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12434
