T1  - ENTREPRENEURSHIP OVER THE LIFE CYCLE: WHERE ARE THE YOUNG ENTREPRENEURS?
AU  - Hincapié, Andrés
Y1  - 2020/05/01
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2020/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12436
T2  - International Economic Review
